Public route are accessible to all user but private routes require authentication (like login);

Public Route: 
-------------

A public route can be accessed by any user, whether they are logged in or not. Examples:
-Login Page
-Signup Page
-Home Page


Example of a Public Route:
-------------------------- 

A private route is only accessible to authenticated (logged-in) users. If the user is not logged in, they will be redirected to the login page.